case_circumstances: An unidentified male was a bus passenger traveling from Phoenix to El Paso. He was reported to be behaving abnormally, pacing, yelling, and complaining of stomach pain at the station. On the bus, he locked himself in the bathroom and then jumped out of the window while bus was moving. He was carrying an ID in the name of Domingo M. Morales, which was determined to be a false ID.   Fingerprints have been recently matched to a FBI record under the names Salomon (or Soloman) Delgado Rodriguez, with DOBs of 10 July 1980 and 10 July 1969, and nationality provided to LE was Mexican.  The Tucson Office of the Mexican Consulate is attempting to verify this information.  AAA
